<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٣٠-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَبِهَذَا الإِسْنَادِ أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللَّهِ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">"نَهَى أَنْ يَتَزَعْفَرَ الرَّجُلُ"</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>